    K --> L["Interpret results:<br/>- Does PCO-I&F outperform Kuramoto?<br/>- Does EAPF provide faster lock?<br/>- Which model is most robust to<br/>  frequency mismatch?<br/>- Computational cost differences?"]
    L --> M["Write thesis discussion + conclusion"]

